character: …Okay, this wasn’t what I was expecting when I heard ‘spaghetti’. I was imagining a jumble of thread and yarn, but this is literally just a knitted bowl of spaghetti.
spaghetti: Uh-huh! It’s pretty cool, no?
character: It actually is. Squishy, too.
spaghetti: I’m glad you like it! It’s actually made from magic, so it won’t get dirty or attract bits of random stuff to it!
